    "description": "Tiny House Simulator: Prologue 包含前两项任务，为完整游戏提供引导。虽然我们已经对这次体验进行了打磨，但某些功能和内容将在最终版本中扩展。您的反馈帮助我们改进，感谢您参与并支持我们的旅程！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313780/extras/83f0c487ab83b50383615d3ae174657e.avif?t=1733356915\" width=616 height=71 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313780/extras/392bda1b75baba9dfd3a7c1cbff06e2f.poster.avif?t=1733356915\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313780/extras/392bda1b75baba9dfd3a7c1cbff06e2f.webm?t=1733356915\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>为客户打造迷你房屋：设计独特而温馨的移动迷你房屋。根据客户的品味定制每一间住宅，添加您的个人风格。无论您是建造乡村小屋还是简约风格的房子，都有无尽的选择！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313780/extras/ea1c8f1a95a54f0fd59c28362e4f54fe.avif?t=1733356915\" width=616 height=71 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313780/extras/1dd2f6f5e9d2d49d9e0dd1253de79749.poster.avif?t=1733356915\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313780/extras/1dd2f6f5e9d2d49d9e0dd1253de79749.webm?t=1733356915\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>在一个生机勃勃、充满多样性的岛屿上踏上旅程，每转个弯都能发现新的乐趣。探索西海岸繁华的小镇，或在宁静的中央湖旁放松，亦或者向东南的山区进发。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313780/extras/839e7adb43fd039951467597303d25b8.avif?t=1733356915\" width=616 height=71 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313780/extras/9f17644b8bb617b153167e028e663d75.poster.avif?t=1733356915\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313780/extras/9f17644b8bb617b153167e028e663d75.webm?t=1733356915\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>掌控您如何发展业务、设计迷你房屋，以及探索 Tiny Island。开放世界的游戏玩法为您提供无尽的体验，旨在迎合您独特的风格。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313780/extras/51c46ff2350d044bb885c5b793e75803.avif?t=1733356915\" width=616 height=71 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313780/extras/cfe902188e749e87a1c3f14eb524e8e9.poster.avif?t=1733356915\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313780/extras/cfe902188e749e87a1c3f14eb524e8e9.webm?t=1733356915\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>将您的创作固定在可靠的车辆上，送往岛上满意的客户处。驾驭蜿蜒的道路、如画的小径和具有挑战性的地形，以满足您的最后期限。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313780/extras/7fa1c4da380ec918286b6eda2185e70e.avif?t=1733356915\" width=616 height=71 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313780/extras/9e54439ec1b2a7731a6db528e5f08a56.poster.avif?t=1733356915\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313780/extras/9e54439ec1b2a7731a6db528e5f08a56.webm?t=1733356915\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>管理并发展您的迷你房屋业务。利用辛苦得来的资金升级您的工作坊，购买更好的车辆，或在当地赌场碰碰运气。目标是建造更大、更有趣的家！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313780/extras/468bd07080061353ca585a18df7bdaf8.avif?t=1733356915\" width=616 height=71 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313780/extras/5947fa6356bf2f5f3d13aafcd251776c.poster.avif?t=1733356915\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313780/extras/5947fa6356bf2f5f3d13aafcd251776c.webm?t=1733356915\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>欣赏美丽的景观和景点，包括游乐场、山上的风车及小岛上的灯塔。在沙滩上放松，或探索西南部热闹的机场。<br><br>您准备好迎接终极迷你房屋挑战了吗？开启这个充实的冒险，将您的小规模梦想转变为繁荣的事业！  <br>立即在 Steam 上获取 Tiny House Simulator，开始创造您的梦想之家！",
